            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-145760097" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-145760097" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="145760097">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fxxkthis/">谭不爽</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-11-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很多拉美文学非常牛逼的一点是，就算在开始你就已经知道结尾，但他的描述还是吸引你一字不落不能离手的把书看完</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="190576871">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-190576871" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-190576871" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="190576871">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eastwolf/">穆</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-08-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">略萨同学，历史题材不适合用您最擅长的多线程来回闪烁大法，削弱了叙事力度。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

